|赤緯=-70°14'3"|星座=山案座|星體=疏散星团|星等=13.2|表面亮度=|藍等=}}

'''NGC 2072'''，又記作'''ESO 57-SC4'''，是[[山案座|山案座]]的一個[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]，<ref name="cseligman">{{cite web | url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc20a.htm#2072 | title = NGC 2072 | last = Seligman | first = Courtney | work = Celestial Atlas | language = en | access-date = 2022-03-10 | archive-date = 2018-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181018081148/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc20a.htm#2072 }}</ref>屬於[[大麦哲伦星系|大麦哲伦星系]]<ref name=ngcic>{{cite web|url = http://www.ngcicproject.org/pubdb.htm| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090528100240/http://www.ngcicproject.org/pubdb.htm|archive-date =  2009-05-28|title =  The NGC/IC Project |language = en}}</ref>。1884年12月18日，{{le|彼得羅·巴拉基|Pietro Baracchi}}<!--《世界人名翻译大辞典》-->利用[[墨爾本天文台|墨爾本天文台]]的48寸孔徑[[反射式望遠鏡|反射式望遠鏡]]，發現此星系及[[NGC_2043|NGC 2043]]<ref>{{cite web |first = Wolfgang |last = Steinicke |url = http://www.klima-luft.de/steinicke/ngcic/persons/baracchi.htm |title = Pietro Paolo Giovanni Ernesto Baracchi |access-date = 2022-03-10 |archive-date = 2021-12-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211206011549/http://www.klima-luft.de/steinicke/ngcic/persons/baracchi.htm }}</ref>，其後兩者獲收錄入[[NGC天體表|天體新總表]]。<ref name = "cseligman"/>

